<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Takes as long as it takes. Share and enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Play music in the kitchen. <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1E8LaodrxNOC26?si=4aIi2q8AQi-XlRd-7pQU2g">I recommend this playlist.</a></li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>Cut the avocado in half in the longitudinal axis. Take the core out. Cut the halves into quorters, and peal off the skin.</li>
  <li>Slice up the avocado, and crush the slices with a fork. It does not have to be completely creamy.</li>
  <li>Finely chop the red onion and remove the inside of the salad tomato after cutting it in half. Chop the tomato meat and its skin into very small bits.</li>
  <li>Mix all ingredients and season with salt and pepper to your taste.</li>
  <li>Serve as a dip or on toast.</li>
</ol>
